      "Alice needs to add a few numbers recursively.\n",
      "So she wrote a simple function for adding numbers, and called the same function over and over to achieve her goal."
     ]
    },
    {
     "cell_type": "code",
     "collapsed": false,
     "input": [
      "def alice_adder(num1, num2):\n",
      "\treturn num1 + num2"
     ],
     "language": "python",
     "metadata": {},
     "outputs": [],
     "prompt_number": 1
    },
    {
